snippet.title: Pascal’s Wager Preorder Now!
snippet.description:
Pascal’s Wager is now open for Preorder Via The App Store for iOS! This is an adventure you won’t want to miss! 

Get more information on the game @ https://pw.giant.games 

Preorder@ https://apps.apple.com/app/pascals-wager/id1476649036

Wanting to know more, be part of the community or just ask the Dev's some questions? Follow us!

Discord: https://discord.gg/aXxxENu
Reddit: https://reddit.com/r/PascalsWagerGame
Facebook: https://facebook.com/PascalsWagerGame
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PascalsWager_
Instagram: https://instagram.com/PascalsWagerGame

Game will Support Multiple Languages! English, Russian, Korean, French, Italian, Portuguese, Spanish, Japanese, Simplified Chinese and Traditional Chinese.
